\id 2JN
\h Yaya II
\toc1 Ala xa masenyi firin nde Annabi Yaya naxan s…õb…õ
\toc2 Yaya II
\mt1 Ala xa masenyi firin nde
\mt1 Annabi Yaya naxan s…õb…õ
\imt1 Masenyi nde yi Kitaabui xa fe ra
\ip Annabi Yaya naxa yi bataax…õ firin nde s…õb…õ danxaniyat…î…õ …≤ama nde ma, n…îndi nu rafanxi naxee ma. Wule xaranyi nde nu yensenxi na waxati, a falafe ra a Isa mu nu faxi duni…≤a adama ki ma. Annabi Yaya a masenma danxaniyat…î…õe b…õ a a lanma e xa tondi mixie ra naxee na xaranyi m…î…îli tima.
\ip Yi bataax…õ a masenma danxaniyat…î…õ birin b…õ a xanunteya findixi Ala kolonmae xa t…înxuma nan na. Ala wama won xa findi mixie ra naxee e bore xanuxi. Mixi naxan na tondi na yaamari ra, a bara tondi Ala fan na. Ala xa won mali alako xanunteya xa lu won b…î…≤…õ ma. Amina.
\mt1 Ala xa masenyi firin nde
\mt1 Annabi Yaya naxan s…õb…õ
\cl Sora
\c 1
\s1 N…îndi
\p 
\v 1 N tan wo xa kuntigi bara wo x…õ…õbu, wo tan naxee findixi danxaniyat…î…õ …≤ama sugandixi ra, a nun wo boore naxee bara n…îndi kolon. Wo rafan n tan nun n…îndi kolonyi birin ma,
\v 2 barima n…îndi luma won b…î…≤…õ ma abadan.
\v 3 Baba Ala nun a xa Di Isa, a xa Mixi Sugandixi, e xa hinn…õ won na, e xa kinikini won ma, e xa b…î…≤…õsa fi won ma n…îndi nun xanunteya kui.
\p 
\v 4 N bara s…õ…õwa ki fanyi, barima ndee na wo ya ma naxee …≤…õr…õfe Baba Ala xa n…îndi kira x…în ma a xa s…õriy…õ ki ma.
\v 5 Danxaniyat…î…õ fanyie, n bara wo mayandi, won xa won bore xanu. N na naxan s…õb…õfe yi ki, yaamari n…õ…õn…õ mu a ra. Won bara na s…õriy…õ kolon kabi a f…îl…õ.
\v 6 Xanunteya nan ya, wo xa bira Ala xa s…õriy…õ f…îx…î ra. Wo lan n…õ wo xa Ala xa yaamarie rabatu, al…î wo a m…õxi ki nax…õ kabi a f…îl…õ.
\p 
\v 7 Mixi gbegbe wama wo madaxufe, a falafe ra a Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi Isa mu faxi duni…≤a adama ki ma. Na mixi madaxui m…î…îli findixi Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi yaxui nan na.
\v 8 Wo xa fe birin naba alako wo naxa gan wo xa wali munafanyi ra. Wo xa kata wo xa sare kamalixi s…ît…î.
\p 
\v 9 Mixi naxan fe gb…õt…õ suxuma, a mu bira Ala xa Mixi Sugandixi xa xaranyi f…îx…î ra, na kanyi mu Ala kolon. Naxan birama a f…îx…î ra, a bara Baba Ala nun a xa Di kolon.
\v 10 Xa karam…îx…î nde sa fa wo yire yi xaranyi xanbi, wo naxa a ras…õn…õ, wo naxa a x…õ…õbu,
\v 11 xa na mu a ra wo fan bara lu a xa wali …≤aaxi kui.
\p 
\v 12 N wama fe gbegbe falafe wo b…õ, k…în…î n mu wama na rabafe s…õb…õli ra, fo won xa lu yire keren, won xa d…õ masara, alako won ma s…õ…õw…õ xa kamali.
\v 13 Wo boore danxaniyat…î…õe bara wo x…õ…õbu.
